overview: You've heard of "tight security," but how about Feds in your bed? Well, that's the problem facing the owner of a high-class brothel played by the lovely Kaylan Nicole. It seems Secret Service agents are spying on a suspected terrorist in the house next door. The only trouble is the agents are getting some major distractions. You know how those all-night stakeouts can be! Now see how some "pros" operate!
tagline: Kaylan Nicole is back. And she hasn't missed a beat.
title: Upbeat Love 2
